body_html:
@ibab if you want, feel free to grab my changes into your PR.

BTW, how was your PHD work? Good luck!

On Sat, May 14, 2016 at 4:30 PM, Igor Babuschkin notifications@github.com
wrote:

I rebased my changes on top of master, fixing the resulting merge
conflicts and applying @girving https://github.com/girving's comments.
In order to get the tests to pass, I've converted a few more of the ops to
complex128, but I tried to keep it minimal in order to not conflict with
@hunkim https://github.com/hunkim's PR too much.

Also, I didn't commit the ops.pbtxt, as it seems that there are currently
some unrelated ops on master for which the ops.pbtxt hasn't been
committed yet.

—
